                "反射"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/Collection/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/Collection/",
            "title": "Collection",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"arraylist-和linkedlist的区别是什么\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#arraylist-和linkedlist的区别是什么\">#</a> ArrayList 和LinkedList的区别是什么</h2>\n<h3 id=\"底层数据结构\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#底层数据结构\">#</a> 底层数据结构</h3>\n<p>● ArrayList 是动态数组的数据结构实现</p>\n<p>● LinkedList 是双向链表的数据结构实现</p>\n<h3 id=\"操作数据效率\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#操作数据效率\">#</a> 操作数据效率</h3>\n<p>● ArrayList按照下标查询的时间复杂度O(1)【内存是连续的,根据寻址公式】,LinkedList不支持下标查询查找(未知索引):ArrayList需要遍历,链表也需要链表,时间复杂度都是O(n)<br />\n新增和删除<br />\n● ArrayList尾部插入和删除,时间复杂度是O(1);其他部分增删需要挪动数组,时间复杂度是O(n)<br />\n● LinkedList头尾节点增删时间复杂度是O(1),其他都需要遍历链表,时间复杂度是O(n)</p>\n<h3 id=\"空间占用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#空间占用\">#</a> 空间占用</h3>\n<p>ArrayList底层是数组，内存连续，节省内存<br />\nLinkedList是双向链表，需要存储数据和两个指针，更占用内存</p>\n<h3 id=\"线程安全\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#线程安全\">#</a> 线程安全</h3>\n<p>● ArrayList和LinkedList都不是线程安全的如果需要保证线程安全,有两种方案:</p>\n<p>● 在方法内使用,局部变量则是线程安全的</p>\n<p>● 使用线程安全的ArrayList和LinkedList</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">List</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">Object</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> syncArrayList</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> Collections</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">synchronizedList</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">new</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> ArrayList</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">List</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">Object</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> syncLinkedList</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> Collections</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">synchronizedList</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">new</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> LinkedList</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java",
                "集合",
                "Java",
                "Collection",
                "集合"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-CAS/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-CAS/",
            "title": "线程安全-CAS",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>CAS = Compare And Swap（比较并交换）</p>\n<p>是典型的乐观锁</p>\n<h2 id=\"它的原子性\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#它的原子性\">#</a> 它的原子性</h2>\n<p>CAS操作是CPU的原子指令，所以<strong>不会被线程切换打断</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"java中的cas\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#java中的cas\">#</a> java中的CAS</h2>\n<p>Atomic类都是CAS的实现</p>\n<h2 id=\"优点\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#优点\">#</a> 优点</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1️⃣-无锁性能高\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1️⃣-无锁性能高\">#</a> 1️⃣ 无锁（性能高）</h3>\n<p>CAS 是 <strong>非阻塞算法</strong>。</p>\n<p>不会像 <code>synchronized</code>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>线程阻塞</li>\n<li>线程唤醒</li>\n<li>上下文切换</li>\n</ul>\n<p>所以性能通常更高。</p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"2️⃣-不会发生死锁\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2️⃣-不会发生死锁\">#</a> 2️⃣ 不会发生死锁</h3>\n<p>CAS 没有锁。</p>\n<p>自然 <strong>不会死锁</strong>。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java",
                "并发",
                "Java",
                "并发"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-synchronized%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-synchronized%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97/",
            "title": "线程安全-synchronized关键字",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"synchronized关键字\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#synchronized关键字\">#</a> synchronized关键字</h2>\n<p>用于在多线程环境下保证线程的安全性，它可以保证在同一时刻只有一个线程可以进入被synchronized修饰的方法或代码块。（还好我想了一下，只保证在一个jvm进程内有效）</p>\n<p>也就是说特性有两点，这也是<strong>线程安全的原理</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>互斥</p>\n<p>同一时间只有一个线程可以进入代码块</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>可见性</p>\n<p>必须刷新到主内存，其他线程可见</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用\">#</a> 使用</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>修饰实例方法，锁对象是<strong>实例this</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">public</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> synchronized</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> void</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> method</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//等价</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">public</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> void</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> method</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">    synchronized</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\">this</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修饰静态方法，锁对象是<strong>Class对象</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">public</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> static</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> synchronized</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> void</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> method</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//等价</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">synchronized</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">ClassName</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">class</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修饰代码块，任意对象，关键在于锁的是对象，不是代码</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>synchronized(lock) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    // critical section</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"底层实现\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#底层实现\">#</a> 底层实现</h3>\n<p>获取锁的过程就是获取monitor对象的过程</p>\n<p>monitor对象的话里面有三个队列</p>\n<p>Monitor<br />\n├── Owner (当前持有锁的线程)<br />\n├── EntryList (等待锁的线程)<br />\n└── WaitSet (调用 wait() 的线程)</p>\n<p>当调用notify()方法之后，WaitSet里面的对象会重新进入Entrylist里面，重新竞争锁</p>\n<p>JVM字节码中，获取monitor依靠这两个jvm指令<br />\n<code>monitorenter</code><br />\n<code>monitorexit</code></p>\n<p><code>monitorexit</code>指令会存在两个，就像try catch中的finally一样，防止因为错误而不解锁</p>\n<p>线程进入<br />\n↓<br />\n尝试获得Monitor<br />\n↓<br />\n成功 → 执行代码<br />\n失败 → 阻塞<br />\n↓<br />\n释放Monitor</p>\n<h3 id=\"锁升级\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#锁升级\">#</a> 锁升级</h3>\n<p>无锁<br />\n↓（一直是A线程来，不用cas）<br />\n偏向锁<br />\n↓(出现了B线程,CAS + 自旋获取锁）<br />\n轻量级锁<br />\n↓(自旋很多次仍然拿不到锁，使用Monitor，会阻塞线程，进入内核态）<br />\n重量级锁</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>锁</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>偏向锁</td>\n<td>只有一个线程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>轻量级锁</td>\n<td>少量竞争</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>重量级锁</td>\n<td>多线程竞争</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"对象头mark-wordoptional\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#对象头mark-wordoptional\">#</a> 对象头mark word（optional）</h3>\n<p>在64位JVM中，大概存：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>锁信息<br />\nGC年龄<br />\nhashcode<br />\n线程ID<br />\n偏向锁标志</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>加锁就是修改对象头的线程ID</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java",
                "并发",
                "Java",
                "并发"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B/",
            "title": "线程",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h3 id=\"线程的创建\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#线程的创建\">#</a> 线程的创建</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>继承 Thread 类（Java单继承机制，不推荐）。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>//就是继承，重写run，然后start()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>class MyThread extends Thread &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    @Override</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    public void run() &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        System.out.println(\"线程执行\");</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>new MyThread().start();</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>实现 Runnable 接口（最常用，无返回值）。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>//Runnable就是Thread构造函数的一个参数</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>class MyRunnable implements Runnable &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    @Override</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    public void run() &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        System.out.println(\"线程执行\");</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>new Thread(new MyRunnable()).start();</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>实现 Callable 接口配合 FutureTask，(有返回值，能抛出异常）。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>//这里相当于上面的run方法，返回一个3</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>Callable&#x3C;Integer> task = () -> 1 + 2;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>//futureTask是适配器，因为Thread构造要传Runnable</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>FutureTask&#x3C;Integer> futureTask = new FutureTask&#x3C;>(task);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>new Thread(futureTask).start();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>Integer result = futureTask.get();</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>通过线程池创建（真实项目中的唯一规范做法）。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">ExecutorService</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> pool</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> Executors</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">newFixedThreadPool</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">5</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">pool</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">submit</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> -</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">    System</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">out</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">println</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">线程执行</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#125;</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"线程的生命周期\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#线程的生命周期\">#</a> 线程的生命周期</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>新建</li>\n<li>运行</li>\n<li>阻塞</li>\n<li>等待</li>\n<li>超时等待</li>\n<li>终止</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"常见方法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#常见方法\">#</a> 常见方法</h2>\n<h3 id=\"sleep\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#sleep\">#</a> sleep()</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>让线程休眠</li>\n<li>不释放锁</li>\n<li>Thread类</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"wait\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#wait\">#</a> wait()</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>让线程进入等待状态</li>\n<li>会释放锁</li>\n<li>会被notify()/notifyAll()唤醒</li>\n<li>必须在synchronized中</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"wait和sleep的区别\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#wait和sleep的区别\">#</a> wait()和sleep()的区别</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>对比点</th>\n<th><code>wait()</code></th>\n<th><code>sleep()</code></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>所属类</td>\n<td><code>Object</code> 类的方法</td>\n<td><code>Thread</code> 类的方法</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>是否释放锁</td>\n<td><strong>会释放锁</strong></td>\n<td><strong>不会释放锁</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>使用位置</td>\n<td>必须在 <strong>synchronized 同步块/方法</strong> 中使用</td>\n<td>可以在任何地方使用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>唤醒方式</td>\n<td>需要 <code>notify()</code> / <code>notifyAll()</code></td>\n<td>时间到了自动恢复</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>使用目的</td>\n<td><strong>线程间通信</strong></td>\n<td><strong>让线程休眠一段时间</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"join\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#join\">#</a> join()</h3>\n<p>等待某个线程执行完</p>\n<h3 id=\"notify和notifyall\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#notify和notifyall\">#</a> notify()和notifyAll()</h3>\n<p>随机唤醒一个等待线程和唤醒所有等待线程</p>\n<h4 id=\"为什么必须在synchronized中\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#为什么必须在synchronized中\">#</a> 为什么必须在synchronized中</h4>\n<p>IllegalMonitorStateException异常</p>\n<p>因为它们操作的是对象的 Monitor 等待队列，只有持有对象锁的线程才能调用</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java",
                "并发",
                "Java",
                "并发"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-volatile%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-volatile%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97/",
            "title": "线程安全-volatile关键字",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"核心语义\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#核心语义\">#</a> 核心语义</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>可见性</li>\n<li>有序性（禁止指令重排）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>volatile 不保证原子性</p>\n<h2 id=\"volatile的可见性\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#volatile的可见性\">#</a> volatile的可见性</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>线程修改变量<br />\n必须立即写回主内存</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>其他线程：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>读取变量<br />\n必须从主内存读取</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"jmmjava内存模型的happens-before\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#jmmjava内存模型的happens-before\">#</a> JMM（java内存模型）的happens-before</h2>\n<p><code>volatile</code> 实际上是通过 <strong>happens-before 规则</strong>工作的。</p>\n<p>volatile 写<br />\nhappens-before<br />\nvolatile 读</p>\n<p>为了实现这个 happens-before 关系，JVM 会在 <code>volatile</code> 操作周围插入 <strong>内存屏障（memory barrier）</strong>：</p>\n<p>内存屏障一般有四种</p>\n<ol>\n<li>LoadLoad</li>\n<li>StoreStore</li>\n<li>LoadStore</li>\n<li>StoreLoad</li>\n</ol>\n<p>意思：（屏障前面的什么操作）（屏障后面的什么操作）不能重排序，load-读，store-写</p>\n<h2 id=\"不保证原子性\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#不保证原子性\">#</a> 不保证原子性</h2>\n<p>多线程时可能这样：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>线程A 读取 count=0<br />\n线程B 读取 count=0<br />\n线程A 写回 1<br />\n线程B 写回 1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>最终结果：</p>\n<p>count = 1</p>\n<p>也就是说<strong>线程不安全</strong></p>\n<p><code>volatile</code> 适合：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>状态标志</strong></li>\n<li><strong>单次写，多次读</strong></li>\n<li><strong>不依赖当前值的赋值</strong></li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java",
                "并发",
                "Java",
                "并发"
            ]
        },
