            "id": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/Collection/ArrayList/",
            "url": "https://751200.github.io/2026/03/12/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/Collection/ArrayList/",
            "title": "ArrayList",
            "date_published": "2026-03-12T09:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"变量\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#变量\">#</a> 变量</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t//默认的容量大小，这个会赋值给size</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private static final int DEFAULT_CAPACITY = 10;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span> \t//新建对象时传入的size为0就会用这给elementData赋值</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private static final Object[] EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA = &#123;&#125;;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    //无参构造用，新对象会先分配空数组而不是10大小的数组</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private static final Object[] DEFAULT_EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA = &#123;&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    //数据本体了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    transient Object[] elementData;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t//记录当前大小</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private int size;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"构造函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#构造函数\">#</a> 构造函数</h2>\n<h3 id=\"指定容量arraylistint-initialcapacity\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#指定容量arraylistint-initialcapacity\">#</a> 指定容量ArrayList(int initialCapacity)</h3>\n<p>指定 initialCapacity&gt;0时就是新建数组，</p>\n<p>=0时就赋值成员变量<code>EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA</code></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">   \t/**</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     * Constructs an empty list with the specified initial capacity.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     *</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     * </span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">@param</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">  initialCapacity</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">  the initial capacity of the list</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     * </span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">@throws</span><span style=\"color:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\"> IllegalArgumentException</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> if the specified initial capacity</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     *         is negative</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">     */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">     public</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> ArrayList</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">int</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> initialCapacity</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">        if</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">initialCapacity </span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">></span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">        \t//指定了大小，新建对应大小的数组</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\">            this</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">elementData</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> new</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> Object</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">[</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">initialCapacity</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">]</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">        </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#125;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> else</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> if</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">initialCapacity </span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">==</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">        \t//大小为0赋值空数组</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A65E2B;--shiki-dark:#C99076\">            this</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">elementData</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">        </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#125;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> else</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">            throw</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> new</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> IllegalArgumentException</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">Illegal Capacity: </span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">+</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">                                               initialCapacity</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">        </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"无参arraylist\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#无参arraylist\">#</a> 无参ArrayList()</h3>\n<p>新建的时候是赋值成员变量的默认空数组<code>DEFAULTCAPACITY_EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA</code>，</p>\n<p>这里是没有设置size的</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>    /**</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * Constructs an empty list with an initial capacity of ten.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    public ArrayList() &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    \t//新建的时候是空的</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        this.elementData = DEFAULTCAPACITY_EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"从collection对象构建arraylistcollection-extends-e-c\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#从collection对象构建arraylistcollection-extends-e-c\">#</a> 从collection对象构建<code>ArrayList(Collection&lt;? extends E&gt; c)</code></h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>    /**</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * Constructs a list containing the elements of the specified</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * collection, in the order they are returned by the collection's</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * iterator.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     *</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * @param c the collection whose elements are to be placed into this list</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     * @throws NullPointerException if the specified collection is null</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>     */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    public ArrayList(Collection&#x3C;? extends E> c) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        elementData = c.toArray();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        if ((size = elementData.length) != 0) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            // c.toArray might (incorrectly) not return Object[] (see 6260652)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            if (elementData.getClass() != Object[].class)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>                elementData = Arrays.copyOf(elementData, size, Object[].class);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        &#125; else &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            // replace with empty array.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            this.elementData = EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"扩容机制\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#扩容机制\">#</a> 扩容机制</h2>\n<h3 id=\"第一次扩容\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#第一次扩容\">#</a> 第一次扩容</h3>\n<p>可以看到默认无参，以及指定大小为0的情况下，虽说赋予的数组不同但都是空数组</p>\n<p>最终扩容后为10大小</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>\tpublic boolean add(E e)&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\t//确保内部容量</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\tensureCapacityInternal(size+1)//这里第一次size是0，所以传入参数为1</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\telementData[size++] = e;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\treturn true;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\tprivate void ensureCapacityInternal(int minCapacity)&#123;//这里上面传如参数是1</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\tensureExplicitCapacity(calculateCapacity(elementData,minCapacity))</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\tprivate static int calculateCapacity(Object[] elementData, int minCapacity)&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\tif(elementData == DEFAULTCAPACITY_EMPTY_ELEMENTDATA)&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\t\treturn Math.max(DEFAULT_CAPACITY,minCapacity);//(10,1)无参 第一次的时候</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\t&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t\treturn minCapacity</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>\t&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>  private void ensureExplicitCapacity(int minCapacity) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        modCount++;//用来并发快速失败</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        // overflow-conscious code</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        if (minCapacity - elementData.length > 0)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            grow(minCapacity);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private void grow(int minCapacity) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        int oldCapacity = elementData.length;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        int newCapacity = oldCapacity + (oldCapacity >> 1);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        if (newCapacity - minCapacity &#x3C; 0)//第一次会进</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            newCapacity = minCapacity;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        if (newCapacity - MAX_ARRAY_SIZE > 0)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            newCapacity = hugeCapacity(minCapacity);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            //复制数组到新空间</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        elementData = Arrays.copyOf(elementData, newCapacity);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    private static int hugeCapacity(int minCapacity) &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        if (minCapacity &#x3C; 0) // overflow</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            throw new OutOfMemoryError();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        return (minCapacity > MAX_ARRAY_SIZE) ?</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            Integer.MAX_VALUE :</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>            MAX_ARRAY_SIZE;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    &#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"第二次扩容添加11个对象时\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#第二次扩容添加11个对象时\">#</a> 第二次扩容（添加11个对象时）</h3>\n<p>参考上面吧，最终变15</p>\n<h2 id=\"数组和list之间的转换\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#数组和list之间的转换\">#</a> 数组和List之间的转换</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">List</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">String</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> list</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> Arrays</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">asList</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">String</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">[</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">]</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> array</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> list</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">toArray</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">new</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> String</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">[</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">list</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">size</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">(</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">)</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">]</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"拷贝\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#拷贝\">#</a> 拷贝</h3>\n<p>● 用Arrays.asList转List后,如果修改了数组内容,list受影响吗</p>\n<p>影响，只是吧list对象里面的elementData指向了该数组</p>\n<p>● List用toArray转数组后,如果修改了List内容,数组受影响吗</p>\n<p>不影响</p>\n<h2 id=\"快速失败机制\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#快速失败机制\">#</a> 快速失败机制</h2>\n<p>内部变量modCount（记录集合被修改的次数）</p>\n<p>expectedModCount 是<strong>迭代器（Iterator）内部特有的一个变量</strong>。它就像是迭代器在开始工作前，给集合的状态拍的一张**“快照”**</p>\n<p>当执行某些操作，比如遍历移除的时候会先执行checkForCommodification()方法，最后modCount++</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-text\"><span class=\"line\"><span>final void checkForComodification() &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    // 迭代器开始对比：集合现在的修改次数 vs 我小本本上记的次数</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    if (modCount != expectedModCount)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>        throw new ConcurrentModificationException(); // 如果对不上，直接罢工报错！</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n",
